{"tid":740122,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"分享一個兒時不安夢","createTime":"2018-07-12T15:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T15:30:18.000Z","uid":194552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c83b1b83ad93f366cd66c49e02f20b4d6dbbebe5","tid":740122,"uid":194552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:16:23.000Z","msg":"細細個陣 間唔中就會發呢個夢 持續左6.7年<br />\n<br />\n所以我都而家都記得好清楚<br />\n<br />\n個夢境是咁的<br />\n<br />\n周圍都係漆黑一片 乜都冇<br />\n<br />\n我個人會浮係半空中[大概兩三層樓高]<br />\n<br />\n我望落去就會見到有一大班細路圍左個圈<br />\n<br />\n佢地就唔會郁 但係我就會聽到佢地講野<br />\n<br />\n佢地講野講得好快 而且都唔係屬於人類嘅語言<br />\n<br />\n因為我一句都聽唔到講緊乜 佢地講嘅野會令到我好不安<br />\n<br />\n當我扎醒嘅時候 我個人己經不停咁喊緊<br />\n<br />\n全身都係汗 心緒不寧 <br />\n<br />\n每次發呢個夢都要揾我老母一齊訓先訓得着<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0e9c49feeadb329391eea525432f9b2ceaaa68","tid":740122,"uid":176472,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/231803_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F231803_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1d14fe1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc6ad47a5e74d25664c3e7b95f8a7b25af65223d","tid":740122,"uid":194552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c0e9c49feeadb329391eea525432f9b2ceaaa68","tid":740122,"uid":176472,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/231803_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F231803_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1d14fe1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:22:38.000Z","msg":"巴打 唔好咁應景 好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae430693bac27cef43b11658a17355f25d79f8e3","tid":740122,"uid":176472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc6ad47a5e74d25664c3e7b95f8a7b25af65223d","tid":740122,"uid":194552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c0e9c49feeadb329391eea525432f9b2ceaaa68","tid":740122,"uid":176472,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/231803_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F231803_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1d14fe1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:22:38.000Z","msg":"巴打 唔好咁應景 好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:25:14.000Z","msg":"你前世可能住史達林，夢到上世畫面好正常渣"},{"pid":"83d8c920954860d381f3f8c8d8ae134b431ad167","tid":740122,"uid":159997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:30:18.000Z","msg":"勁不安"}]}